reasons.job: User ka job priority expire ho gaya. Iska matlab user queue mein bahut der tak tha job priority ke liye aur system ne unhe queue se nikal diya.
reasons.kicked: User ko ek staff member ne diye gaye reason ke saath kick kiya.
reasons.overflow: FiveM ke dwara cheaters se server ko spam hone se bachane ke liye safety measure.
reasons.reloading_game: User ne 'localGame' command ka upyog karke ek single-player game load kiya F8 console mein ya similar.
reasons.restart: User ko server ne kick kiya kyunki server restart ho raha tha.
reasons.timeout: User ki server se connection timeout ho gayi. Ye aksar tab hota hai jab internet connectivity drop hoti hai.

staff_statistics.description_chinese: Aapke yogdan ka ek vistaarit record, jo samajik samarasata aur pragati ke liye Party dwaara dekha gaya hai. Yaad rahe, har kriya aapke samuhik bhavishya ke prati samarpan ko darshati hai.
staff_statistics.footer: Aapke karya OP-FW ki safalta aur vriddhi mein yogdaan dete hain. OP-Framework ke vishwasniya pranaliyon ke madhyam se, aapke prayason ko hamare saanjhe pragati ke roop mein pehchana jata hai aur manaya jata hai. Teamwork uplabdhi ko prerit karta hai, aur samarpan uttamta ko nirmit karta hai. OP-FW ko mahima!
staff_statistics.footer_chinese: Har karya jo aap karte hain aapki wafadari aur pratibaddhata ka pramaan hai Party ke liye. Pranali ki chaukanni nazron ke neeche, aapke yogdan hamare saanjhe pragati ke roop mein darj aur manaya jata hai. Aagya ka palan samarasata sunishchit karta hai, aur chaukannapan samriddhi ki guarantee deta hai. CCP ko mahima!
staff_statistics.level_0_description: Yadyapi aapne staff path par kadam rakha hai, aapki kshamata abhi tak soyi hui aur avikrit hai. Aap shikshakon ki fusahaton se gyaan prapt karte hain aur curiosity ke saath rajya ki urjaon ko apne ird-gird ghoomte hue dekhte hain. Mahanata ke beej aapke pakad mein hain, aage badhne ke liye intezaar karte hue.
staff_statistics.level_10_description: Kahaniyan aapke adbhut udgaman ke baare mein batati hain, ek prakash jo keval apni upasthiti se sabse bhayankar tufaanon ko shaant kar deta hai. Aapke staff ki urja ki chamak har kone mein gunjti hai, aapki dekh-rekh mein unbreakable ekta ka nirman karti hai. Is manaviya shakti ke shikhar par, aap har dridhnishchay ke saath rajya ki kismat ko akar dete hain.
staff_statistics.level_1_description: Antatah, staff magic ki pehli chamak aapke haathon mein chamakti hai, chhoti server samasyaon ko hal karne ke liye aapki pratikriyaon ko margdarshit karti hai. Aap tayyar hain kisi chhoti jhagda ko shaant karne ya chhanbhin ashaanti ko shant karne ke liye, aapki kshamata ko sabit karne ke liye utsuk hain. Har sahayata ke liye pukar ke saath gupt bandhan majboot hota hai, unche kadre ke prabhootv ka vachan jagata hai.
staff_statistics.level_2_description: Naazuk dhaaraon ko apnate hue jo server ko roop dete hain, aap nipunata se reports aur anushasanik kadam uthane ka kaushal dikhaate hain. Aapki sanchit avastha aur tezi se ki gayi samadhanon se aafra-tafri ko kampan hota hai aur shanti sthapit rahti hai. Har kriya aapko realm ke tapestry mein gehraai tak bunti hai, aapke sankalp ko iska samarthan deta hai ki aap iski sadbhavna ko surakshit rakhein.
staff_statistics.level_3_description: Aapka arcane wards aur banishing incantations par niyantran server ko ek sthir shanti mein sthapit karta hai. Dushkritya karne wale aapki satarkta se rook jaate hain, aur aapka chamakta hua staff ek adhikar ka pratik hai. Chhupi hui chhaayon ke saamne bhi, aapki atal samarpan aafra-tafri ko vijay mein badal deti hai.
staff_statistics.level_4_description: Andhkaar ke kone-kone se, aap nigrani rakhte hain, us halke se sharaarat ke jhalak par jo realm ko khatrey mein daalti hai. Tezi se ki gayi pratishodh aur sahi samay par ki gayi hastakshep aapki bhoomika ko ek dridh rakshak ke roop mein darshate hain, yeh sunishchit karte hue ki aapke kshetra mein koi shatru zyada der tak na tik sake. Aapki satark nazar ke neeche aadesh aur aafra-tafri ke beech ka parda surakshit bana rehta hai.
staff_statistics.level_5_description: Divya shaktiyan aapke faisle ko margdarshan karti hain, aapko kosmik kripa ke saath sadbhavna lagu karne ka adhikar deti hain. Realm aapke santulit faislon ki or dekhta hai, aapki is kshamata par vishwas karta hai ki aap vivad ko daba sakte hain aur jo avashyak hai unka uthaan kar sakte hain. Har din ke saath, aapka astral urja par maharat badhta hai, staff aur players ke liye marg prakaashit karta hai.
staff_statistics.level_6_description: Aapka staff narkiya shakti se gungunata hai, vipattijanak shaktiyon ko tezi se dur kar deta hai. Aapka naam sunte hi asantusht logon mein bhay ki laharen fail jati hain, kyunki ve jaante hain ki aapka prakop kisi ko nahi bakshata jo rajya ko bigadne ki himmat karta hai. Fir bhi itni shakti ka istemal karte hue, aap nyay ko dhyan mein rakhte hain, sunishchit karte hain ki yah sahi aur dridhata se diya jaye.
staff_statistics.level_7_description: Divya adhikar ka prakashit karte hue, aap rajya ke rakshakon ko sangathit karte hain aur ashaanti ko pakadne se pehle hi shant kar dete hain. Aapki mahan hastakshepon ki fufkar door tak jaati hai, aapki sthiti ko sabke liye ek margdarshak tareeke se majboot karti hai. Aapke samarth haathon mein, server ka bhavishya chamakdar rehta hai, bahar ki andhkaar se anchaal nahi.
staff_statistics.level_8_description: Aap roshni aur andhkaar ke beech ki seema par chalte hain, vyavastha ke chhupay dhagon ko padte hain pehle ki ve phat padein. Tez freeze aur maharathi kicks aapki shanti banaye rakhne ki pratibaddhata ko pramanit karte hain, atka hua khatra chhodne ka koi avasar nahi dete. Aapki sukshmata aur shakti ka samavesh sunishchit karta hai ki aapke rajya mein rehne wale sab log samarasya mein rahen.
staff_statistics.level_9_description: Anant yuddhon ke maadhyam se, aapki maharath maanavik seemaon ko paar kar chuki hai, rananeetik chaturai ko ek atal naitik disha ke saath mila kar. Trolls aur pareshan karne wale aapke peeche gaayab ho jaate hain, har ban ya mute ek santulit pratishodh ka kalatmak stroke hai. Is uchh sthiti mein, aapki samarpan rajya ki atoot pratikarshilata ka pramaan hai.
staff_statistics.title: Karmachaari Sankhiki
